{"tid":1762030,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"打擾嗮各位手足，想問下香港印刷書嘅常用字型係邊種？","createTime":"2019-11-29T09:56:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T17:24:52.000Z","uid":221312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f5058927dc205800154f18aeff51031e5375b5ab","tid":1762030,"uid":221312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T09:56:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DXCnQrS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDXCnQrS.png&h=35ca0a0e&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6EpaeTX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6EpaeTX.png&h=f0366e4d&s={SIZE}\" /> 如圖，電腦常用嘅新細明體，個「骨」字上面向右冇問題啦，但下面個「月」好難睇，但圖片入邊好正規，係我地手寫嘅習慣黎。另外個「權」字，草花頭唔分；「這」字入邊個「辶」個底係尖嘅。我穩黎穩去，最接近呢種字型得「昭源甄黑體」，但昭源嘅「權」字的草花頭係分嘅，唯獨是圖片呢種唔分。就想問下有冇人知呢種字型個名？？我見好多香港出嘅書都係呢種字型，無奈查唔到出處。"},{"pid":"b9f4c081b266f084adb3473d5113b233acecc7a7","tid":1762030,"uid":54627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T12:48:37.000Z","msg":"蒙納宋體同蒙納黑宋（應該係）<br />\n香港正規嘅Publication好多時都用呢隻或者蒙納黑體"},{"pid":"69db7e5a9e7f81032451c067ed8a88222cf57d11","tid":1762030,"uid":157508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T17:24:52.000Z","msg":"昭源甄黑體你唔講我都唔知<br />\n我用開「源樣黑體」系列<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://github.com/ButTaiwan/genyog-font/tree/master/TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2FButTaiwan%2Fgenyog-font%2Ftree%2Fmaster%2FTW&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbY95k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=f3fc66dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/ButTaiwan/genyog-font/tree/master/TW</a>"}]}